Package: smartGSEA
Title: Simplified Gene Set Enrichment Analysis from DESeq2
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Glady Hazitha", "Samuel", , "glady.samuel@uconn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A user-friendly wrapper for clusterProfiler that simplifies GSEA 
    workflows. Handles DESeq2 results directly, auto-detects organisms, properly 
    filters on adjusted p-values, and provides easy comparison functions. Supports 
    both model organisms and custom pathway annotations for non-model organisms.
